course_title: Preparation for a Career in Writing

sections.comments: For CRWR Majors only. All CRWR Winter Term 1 (September-December) courses/sections will be held online. This particular course will be asynchronous (modules to be posted on Mondays), with an optional component to meet on Zoom for live discussion weekly on Wednesdays at 10am Pacific Time.
